{"title_page": "Kim Sang-wook (fencer)", "text_new": "{{short description|South Korean fencer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Korean name|Kim}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name             = Kim Sang-wook\n| image            = \n| caption          = \n| headercolor      = lightsteelblue\n| birth_name       = \n| fullname         = \n| nickname         = \n| nationality      = \n| residence        = \n| birth_date       = {{birth date and age|1964|6|13|df=yes}}\n| birth_place      = \n| death_date       = \n| death_place      = \n| height           = \n| weight           = \n| website          = \n| country          = \n| sport            = [[Fencing]]\n| event            = \n| collegeteam      = \n| club             = \n| team             = \n| turnedpro        = \n| coach            = \n| retired          = \n| coaching         = \n| module2          = \n{{Infobox Korean name|child=yes\n| hangul = \uae40\uc0c1\uc6b1\n| hanja  = \u91d1\u5c19\u715c\n| rr     = Gim Sanguk\n| mr     = Kim Sanguk\n}}\n| worlds           = \n| regionals        = \n| nationals        = \n| olympics         = \n| highestranking   = \n| pb               = \n| show-medals      = yes\n}}\n\n'''Kim Sang-wook''' (born 13 June 1964) is a South Korean [[fencing|fencer]]. He competed in the individual and team [[sabre (fencing)|sabre]] events at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"sports-reference\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ki/kim-sang-uk-1.html |title=Kim Sang-Uk |accessdate=25 July 2011}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kim, Sang-wook}}\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:South Korean male fencers]]\n[[Category:Olympic fencers of South Korea]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in fencing]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1986 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1990 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Fencers at th